. // PANEL A RESULTS (confirmed March 2026, gridmin(-2) gridmax(2)):
. //   S1 18mo primary: coef= 0.029  CI=[-0.093, 0.101]  p=0.063
. //   S2 12mo lower:   coef= 0.047  CI=[-0.583, 0.667]  p=0.128
